# API Keys Configuration File
# 
# Add your commercial API keys here in the format:
# API_NAME=your_api_key_here
#
# Supported APIs:
# - DEEPSEEK: DeepSeek API (https://platform.deepseek.com/)
# - ANTHROPIC or CLAUDE: Anthropic Claude API (https://console.anthropic.com/)
# - OPENAI: OpenAI API (https://platform.openai.com/)
# - GOOGLE or GEMINI: Google Gemini API (https://ai.google.dev/)
#   Note: Both GOOGLE and GEMINI are equivalent names for the same API
#
# Example:
# DEEPSEEK=sk-your-deepseek-api-key-here
# ANTHROPIC=sk-ant-your-anthropic-api-key-here
# OPENAI=sk-your-openai-api-key-here
# GEMINI=your-google-api-key-here
# # Or use GOOGLE (both are equivalent):
# # GOOGLE=your-google-api-key-here
#
# Lines starting with # are comments and will be ignored
# Empty lines are also ignored
#
# Security Note: 
# - Never commit this file to version control
# - Keep your API keys secure and private
# - Add .keys to your .gitignore file
